       \t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n    \n       \t\n        \t\t<div id=\"tables\" class=\"panel panel-default\">\n\n\t\t\t\t  \n\n<div>\n\t\n\t\n\t\n</div>\t\t\t\t      \n\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"panel-body\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n                        \n                      Consult Corporations Canada’s database, the source to confirm the existence of a corporation created under a federal corporate law. <br><br> This database does <b>not</b> include corporations created under financial (such as financial institutions, insurance companies or loan and trust companies) or those created under provincial/territorial corporate laws or under foreign corporate laws. For corporations created under provincial/territorial laws, consult <a class=\"\" href=\"https://ised-isde.canada.ca/cc/lgcy/rdrctr.html?pid=rdrct.url77\" title=\"Canada’s Business Registries - opens in a new window\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"help\">Canada’s Business Registries</a>.          \n                    </p>\n   \t\t\t\t\t<p>Once you have completed a transaction with Corporations Canada, it may take several hours for the database to reflect the update.</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t      <div class=\"boxBthin padding8 searchform\">\n\t\t\t\t        <p>Find out how to improve your search results with  \n                          \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n<a class=\"\" href=\"https://ised-isde.canada.ca/cc/lgcy/rdrctr.html?pid=rdrct.url7\" title=\"Search Tips. - opens in a new window\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"help\">Search Tips.</a>\n\n\t\t\t\t      \n\t\t\t\t      </p><div class=\"form-group\">\n\t\t\t\t\t  \t<label></label>\t\n\t\t\t          \t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n\t  <label for=\"corpName\" class=\"\">\n\t  \t\n\t\t    <span class=\"field-name \">\n\t\t      Corporate name\n\t\t    </span> \n\t    \n\t    \n\t    \n\t  </label> \n      <input id=\"corpName\" name=\"corpName\" class=\"form-control \" type=\"text\" value=\"\" size=\"20\">\n    </div>\n  \n\n \n\n\t\t\t          \t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n\t  <label for=\"corpNumber\" class=\"\">\n\t  \t\n\t\t    <span class=\"field-name \">\n\t\t      Corporation number\n\t\t    </span> \n\t    \n\t    \n\t    \n\t  </label> \n      <input id=\"corpNumber\" name=\"corpNumber\" class=\"form-control \" type=\"text\" value=\"\" size=\"10\" maxlength=\"10\">\n    </div>\n  \n\n \n\n\t\t\t          \t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n\t  <label for=\"busNumber\" class=\"\">\n\t  \t\n\t\t    <span class=\"field-name \">\n\t\t      Business number (BN)\n\t\t    </span> \n\t    \n\t    \n\t    \n\t  </label> \n      <input id=\"busNumber\" name=\"busNumber\" class=\"form-control \" type=\"text\" value=\"\" size=\"15\" maxlength=\"15\">\n    </div>\n  \n\n \n\t\t\t\t      \n  \t\t\t\t\t  </div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t      <h3>Additional Search Options</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n  \n  \n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n\t  <label for=\"corpProvince\" class=\"\">\n\t  \t\n\t\t    <span class=\"field-name \">\n\t\t      Province of Registered Office\n\t\t    </span> \n\t    \n\t    \n\t    \n\t  </label> \n      <select id=\"corpProvince\" name=\"corpProvince\" class=\"form-control\">\t\t\t\t            \n\t\t\t              <option value=\"\" selected=\"selected\">\n\t\t\t                Any\n\t\t\t              </option>\n\t\t\t              \n\t\t\t                <option value=\"124-AB\">\n\t\t\t                  Alberta\n\t\t\t 